    "structure": "One-compartment, first-order absorption and elimination",
    "equations": "CL = (theta1*WT*(DMGKG**theta2)*(theta3**CBZ)*(theta4**PHT)* (theta5**PHB))*(1+eta1) KA = theta6 V = theta7*WT Cobs=Cipred+eps1 DMGKG: daily dose VPA in mg/kg/day WT: Total body weight (kg) CBZ: comedication carbamazepine (1:yes, 0:no) PHT: comedication phenytoin (1:yes, 0:no) PHB: comedication phenobarbital (1:yes, 0:no)",
